## Quick Troubleshooting

| Problem | Action |
| --- | --- |
| Waybar or UI inconsistency | `seven repair ux --apply` then `seven hypr apply` |
| Light/dark theme incomplete | `seven theme doctor` then `./install.sh theme light` or `dark` |
| Mini OS app outside isolation | relaunch with `seven profile open <profile>` or a profiled launcher |
| External folder invisible | `seven profile grant-folder <profile> <path> --name <name> --rw` |
| Missing dependencies | `seven profile requirements all --apply --yes` |
| Suspicious mini OS rootfs | `seven profile-rootfs verify all` |
| Windows Bridge not ready | `seven windows setup` |
| Terminal hard to read | `Ctrl+Shift+B`, `Bg` button, or `SEVENOS_TERMINAL_ALPHA=0.75 seven-terminal` |
| Before GitHub push | `seven pre-push` |

